            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In domini nostri Iehsu sit nomine Christi. Anno nativitate eius
                        millesimo centesimo nonagesimo secundo, indictione XI, ydus novembris.
                        Manifestus sum ego <persName>Gerarduccius</persName> quondam
                            <persName>Temi</persName> quia per hanc cartulam (ve)ndo (…)
                            <persName>Alrigo</persName> quondam dicti Temini videlicet medietatem
                        integram pro indiviso unius montis positam in confinibus
                            <placeName>Putei</placeName> in loco ubi dicitur Cruce, cuius tenet unum
                        caput in <rs>via publica</rs>, aliud in terra et <rs>bossco</rs>
                        <persName>Chiarecti</persName>, latus in terra <persName>Fornari</persName>
                        quondam <persName>Uguicioni</persName>, aliud vero latus in terra
                            <persName>Guilielmi</persName> quondam et <persName>Conciati</persName>
                        et <orgName>Sancti Rolenthi</orgName> et <persName>Ianni</persName>, habens
                        in se <rs>vineam</rs> et <rs>olivas</rs> et <rs>ficus</rs>. (…)
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum (…). Actum in Montingnano,
                            <placeName>Sancte Marie Montis</placeName>. Presentia et testimonio
                            <persName>Ayverami</persName> filius <persName>Greppaldi</persName>,
                            <persName>Aliccioni</persName> filius <persName>Romachi</persName>,
                            <persName>Bonaiuti</persName> quondam <persName>Ildebrandini</persName>.
                        Interfuerunt rogati <rs>testes</rs>. Item in presentia suprascriptorum
                        dictus Gerarduccius confitetur vendidisse cum patre suo Teminio predicto
                        Alrigo unam aliam petiolam terre in valle Lingnano, tenens caput in terra
                            <persName>Bononcontri</persName>, aliud in terra ecclesie Sancti
                        Rolenthi, ambo latera in terris <persName>Aldimari</persName>. Et confitetur
                        de ea abuisse pretium soldorum quinque et supena quadraginta soldorum
                        promisit nullo tempore litem neque modestiam (sic) facere suprascripto Arigo
                        nec suo heredi aut cui dederint. Prefatus Gerarduccius hanc cartulam fieri
                        rogavit. (S) Ego <persName>Rubacastellus</persName> domni romanorum
                        imperatoris <rs>iudex ordinarius</rs> et <rs>notarius</rs> hanc cartulam
                        scripsi et dedi.</ab>
